# create-fr — FR authoring context (SAB)

General markup and ID rules for `docs/specs/**/*.md`: [.cursor/rules/docs.mdc](docs.mdc). This file covers **functional requirements only** and must not duplicate [docs/specs/functional-requirements/_template-fr.md](../../docs/specs/functional-requirements/_template-fr.md).

## Sources (order)

1. [Use case registry](../../docs/artifacts/use-case/use-case-registry.md) — UC codes and titles for the “Входные UC” section (**только строки реестра**, без пояснений в скобках; см. шаблон).
2. UC write-ups (including [docs/artifacts/use-case/](../../docs/artifacts/use-case/)) — flows and boundaries for wording and `.СД`.
3. [Conceptual model with attributes](../../docs/artifacts/conceptual-model-with-attributes.md) — entity and attribute names; `` `[Entity]:field` `` in lists.
4. [Glossary](../../docs/artifacts/project-glossary.md); on term mismatch, record explicitly (`Unclear:` / question to analyst).
5. [Project charter](../../docs/artifacts/project-charter.md) — solution scope and constraints.

## Document references

- **Structure, CRUDL table, phrase templates, checklist** — follow [_template-fr.md](../../docs/specs/functional-requirements/_template-fr.md); do not invent a parallel outline.
- **Examples:** [fr-booking.md](../../docs/specs/functional-requirements/fr-booking.md) — объем `.СД` и алгоритмы; [fr-parking-session.md](../../docs/specs/functional-requirements/fr-parking-session.md) — лаконичные **«Входные UC»**, списки атрибутов у ролей, родительский `.СД` в одно предложение, кросс-объектные подпункты `.СД.[имя]`. Остальные `fr-*.md` не каноничны, если расходятся с шаблоном.

## CRUDL and verbs

Canonical C/R/U/D/L mapping and domain variants are in the template table. **D:** default to UC wording (`Удалить`, `Отменить`, etc.). For **Бронирование (Booking)**, prefer **`Отменить`** for cancel/complete semantics, as in `fr-booking.md`. Outside CRUDL, take the action name from the **UC title** in the registry.

## System actions (`.СД`, `.СД.<attribute>`)

The suffix marks **system** behavior (calculations, statuses, derived fields, event reactions), not a user UI action. Do not use “позволять пользователю” phrasing — see the template and `fr-booking.md`.

## Wording (no UC codes in requirement text)

- **UC codes** belong in **«Входные UC»** and in the **FR-\*** registry line (`— UC-x.y`), not in the body of role sections or `## Системы`.
- Requirement text: **condition + object + attributes/algorithms** in domain terms; avoid long parenthetical scenario chains and “воду”.
- Follow [_template-fr.md](../../docs/specs/functional-requirements/_template-fr.md): **Краткость**, **Списки атрибутов у ролей (строгий формат)**, **Входные UC** (строго).

## Conditions and algorithms (attribute-level `.СД.*`)

- Put **conditions, branches, and sources of values** under **`[Object].[Action].СД.[name]`** — «Система должна изменять `[Объект]:[атрибут]` по следующему алгоритму:» or **кросс-объектный** блок «Система должна [глагол] … по следующему алгоритму:» (see template **«Где описывать условия и алгоритмы»**, **«Кросс-объектное действие»**).
- Do not stack algorithms in the parent `[Object].[Action].СД` paragraph beyond **one sentence** (trigger + input); cross-entity effects get their own `.СД.[name]` or a pointer to another FR doc.

## Workflow

1. Collect UCs for the object from the registry; open full UC docs when needed.
2. Reconcile entity and attributes with the conceptual model and glossary.
3. Fill the doc per **_template-fr.md** (TOC, **Входные UC** без хвостов, кандидаты, `FR-*` реестр, роли со **строгими списками**, `## Системы` при необходимости).
4. Align depth: **fr-booking.md** for `.СД` algorithms; **fr-parking-session.md** for concise lists and `Фильтры:`.
5. Self-check against **Чеклист качества** in the template (в т.ч. **Формат списков у ролей**).
6. On substantive FR changes, remind about [traceability-matrix-log.md](../../docs/process/traceability-matrix-log.md) and repo CI policy.

## Link checks

After editing headings or TOC: `npm run lint:md-links` or `node ./scripts/check-markdown-links.mjs` (as in the template).
